data.description: Ask about lender buy-down! Welcome to your new spacious oasis in  scenic Bartram Springs! This immaculate 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home boasts brand-new roofing, ensuring peace of mind for years to come. Nestled conveniently near the serene river, this property offers the perfect blend of nature and comfort. Step inside to discover a wealth of living space, including a generous bonus room, providing the flexibility to accommodate your unique needs. The gourmet kitchen, a true culinary haven, is ready to inspire your inner chef and elevate your dining experience. With ample countertop space and top-notch appliances, meal preparation will be a breeze. Outside, a sprawling backyard awaits, providing ample room for your creative vision. Whether you dream of a lush garden, a tranquil escape.
